    "Delay in LLMs: The real-time performance of LLM also has significant shortcomings.",
    "One example is offline training.",
    "LLMs are frozen after completing pre training and cannot dynamically learn new knowledge at runtime.",
    "(Gao P. et al., 2023) The other is that reasoning relies on historical knowledge.",
    "LLM's reasoning is based on the corpus knowledge captured by the model during training, lacking sensitivity to real-time dynamic information. 3."
